Package ants.missions

Interface Summary
Mission defines which method must be implemented by a mission
 

Class Summary
AttackAntMission This mission is created for attacking enemy ants.
AttackHillMission This mission used for attacking the enemies hills
BaseMission Implements the interface Mission an handles the base tasks of a mission.
ExploreMission Mission for exploring the world
FollowMission This mission is used to let an ant follow an other ant which has already a mission.
GatherFoodMission Mission for gathering a food tile
PathMission this mission is implemented to follow a path defined while creating the class
